{
  "stem": "1965.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Callwood.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Santa.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, as you know, as I previously said, she was taken to the hospital very sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had two operations during that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in a Belgium hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to make that clear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "While she was there, there were about 32 Jewish people in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A disgruntled person denounced the Jews who were in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And unfortunately, my mother was taken away from the hospital bed and placed in the last transport to Auschwitz Birkenau, which was number 28.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When she came there, she told me the stories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I also learned from other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because it was the last transport, primarily the Jewish women there were of Hungarian descent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when you were married or coming with a child, you did not come to be a laborer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You came to be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But if you were single, that's when they would keep you into the camp for labor purposes, until they figured that you couldn't handle it no more because your body couldn't sustain it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they would give you the shower of gas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother was very sweet and tender.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Hungarian women knew that she had three children in hiding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they said to her, we must do whatever we can to keep you surviving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because those children, as long as they are in hiding, and they have not been exterminated, we must make sure that you stay alive so that you can be with them after the war.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, when they were standing in line to have their ration of food, which was skinned potatoes in water, they said to her, why don't you go for a second one?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You need the strength.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she went and asked for a second portion.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
